        <h2><span;>Our Mission</span></h2>
        <p>
          Our goal is to provide an easy way for anyone to discover their creative voice; their inner-Makr. When we collaborate with others, new ideas and inspiration can emerge. We view remixing as a cultural tool that continues the spread of ideas, creativity and inspiration for others to take and build upon. <a href='http://makriohq.tumblr.com/post/28562322358/welcome-to-makr-io' target="_blank">Read more about Makr culture.</a> 
        </p>
        <br/>

        <h2><span;>The Team</span></h2>
        <p>
          The Makr.io team is a bunch of hackers, designers, and internet-lovers living in the Bay Area. When we're not working on Makr or thinking about the internet, you can find us playing video games, eating Otter Pops, or riding our bikes around the neighborhood.
